init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You call the number, and are told to meet your contact at JFK airport in 3 days.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You fly into JFK and immediately notice your contact waiting in the terminal.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You shake his hand and ask "George Washington?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Well, I can't give you the details of why you are here, but I can tell you that a time traveler has received information in the

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: future that a nuclear device will be detonated near here.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was a rudimentary device, but enough to level the area around it.
